Shipping and Delivery Policy for Zarooor

Introduction
At Zarooor, we are committed to delivering your orders promptly and efficiently. This Shipping and Delivery Policy outlines the terms and conditions for the delivery of products purchased through our platform.

Delivery Areas
1. **Service Coverage:**
   - We deliver to locations within our operational areas. You can check service availability for your area during checkout.

2. **Restricted Areas:**
   - Orders cannot be delivered to areas outside our coverage or restricted zones. 

Delivery Times
1. **Standard Delivery:**
   - Orders will be delivered within 1-3 business days, depending on your location and product availability.

2. **Express Delivery:**
   - For eligible locations, we offer same-day or next-day delivery at an additional cost. Availability of this option will be shown at checkout.

3. **Delivery Slots:**
   - You may choose a preferred delivery slot (if available) during checkout.

Order Tracking
1. **Real-Time Updates:**
   - Once your order is confirmed, you will receive a tracking link via email or SMS to monitor the status of your delivery.

2. **Notifications:**
   - We will keep you informed about the orderâ€™s progress, including dispatch and estimated delivery time.

Shipping Charges
1. **Standard Shipping:**
   - Shipping fees may vary based on your location and the total order amount. Free shipping may be offered for orders exceeding a specified amount.

2. **Express Shipping:**
   - Express shipping charges will apply for expedited deliveries. These charges will be displayed at checkout.

Delivery Conditions
1. **Successful Delivery:**
   - A delivery will be considered successful if received by you or an authorized person at the delivery address provided.

2. **Missed Deliveries:**
   - If the delivery attempt fails due to incorrect address or unavailability of the recipient, we will contact you to reschedule. Additional charges may apply for repeated delivery attempts.

3. **Product Inspection:**
   - We recommend inspecting the package at the time of delivery. Report any damage or discrepancies immediately to our delivery personnel or contact customer support.

Shipping Restrictions
1. **Hazardous or Restricted Items:**
   - Certain products, due to legal or logistical constraints, may not be eligible for delivery to all locations. This will be indicated during checkout.

2. **Natural Disruptions:**
   - Deliveries may be delayed due to weather conditions, natural disasters, or other unforeseen circumstances. We will notify you in case of such delays.

Returns and Refunds
1. **Return Policy:**
   - For details on returns and refunds, please refer to our Cancellation and Refund Policy.

2. **Delivery Charges on Returns:**
   - Delivery charges are non-refundable unless the return is due to a product defect or error on our part.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns regarding shipping or delivery, please contact us at:
Email: droghershub2021@gmail.com

Changes to This Policy
We may update this Shipping and Delivery Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.

Thank you for choosing Zarooor. We are dedicated to ensuring your orders reach you quickly and safely!
